rows.label: bf08390100_0010
rows.name:
Well, no way I'd ever have guessed the
World Tree was like this on the inside.

rows.label: bf08390100_0020
rows.name: It definitely appears to be man-made.

rows.label: bf08390100_0030
rows.name: Created by the same civilization as Mors...

rows.label: bf08390100_0040
rows.name: God's birthplace...That's what Shin called it.

rows.label: bf08390100_0050
rows.name: Then did God build this?

rows.label: bf08390100_0060
rows.name: Is he really at the top of this tower? And Eden too?

rows.label: bf08390100_0070
rows.name:
From what we saw in Mors, it seemed like all that stuff
happened a gazillion years ago.

rows.label: bf08390100_0080
rows.name: Or maybe two gazillion, I don't know.

rows.label: bf08390100_0090
rows.name: Not even Divine Beasts live that long.

rows.label: bf08390100_0100
rows.name:
Even Homura and Hikari have never actually met him.
But this tower's right here. It's real...

rows.label: bf08390100_0110
rows.name: So...

rows.label: bf08390100_0120
rows.name: 'Seeing is believing', is the phrase, hm?

rows.label: bf08390100_0130
rows.name:
We'll just have to find out for ourselves.
There's no use speculating.

rows.label: bf08390100_0140
rows.name:
Nia, what's wrong?
Is tummy started rumbling?

rows.label: bf08390100_0150
rows.name: Oh, for the...

rows.label: bf08390100_0160
rows.name:
Every time with you it's 'have you lost
your wallet?' or 'are you hungry?'

rows.label: bf08390100_0165
rows.name: Is that really all you can think of?

rows.label: bf08390100_0170
rows.name: Mehhhh...

rows.label: bf08390100_0180
rows.name:
Wh-wh... T-Tora thought food is only thing that
makes Nia all...um...growly-growly.

rows.label: bf08390100_0190
rows.name: Watch it, furball...

rows.label: bf08390100_0200
rows.name: What is Nia's problem?

rows.label: bf08390100_0210
rows.name:
That's not a nice way to ask, Hana.
But I'll let it slide.

rows.label: bf08390100_0220
rows.name: There's something I want to ask you Blades.

rows.label: bf08390100_0230
rows.name:
Tell the truth...
Have you ever wanted to extend your life?

rows.label: bf08390100_0240
rows.name: Avoid returning to our cores?

rows.label: bf08390100_0250
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: bf08390100_0260
rows.name: That's a tough question...

rows.label: bf08390100_0270
rows.name:
I would like to keep learning about my former selves...
But to keep living after Meleph is dead...

rows.label: bf08390100_0275
rows.name: Oh, I'm sorry...

rows.label: bf08390100_0280
rows.name: No, I understand.

rows.label: bf08390100_0290
rows.name:
*sigh* The idea of living on without her
does not appeal to me.

rows.label: bf08390100_0300
rows.name: Yeah, same here.

rows.label: bf08390100_0310
rows.name: I want my memories of the Prince to be just between us.

rows.label: bf08390100_0320
rows.name: You're going to make me blush, Saika!

rows.label: bf08390100_0330
rows.name: Byakko?

rows.label: bf08390100_0340
rows.name:
As long as I'm by my lady's side till the end...
...then I'm satisfied.

rows.label: bf08390100_0350
rows.name:
Hana is artificial Blade.
So it is very sad for me to think about.

rows.label: bf08390100_0360
rows.name:
When Masterpon is gone, Hana
will be widow.

rows.label: bf08390100_0370
rows.name: Mehhhhh!

rows.label: bf08390100_0380
rows.name: Well, not quite. But I get where you're coming from.

rows.label: bf08390100_0390
rows.name: Homura?

rows.label: bf08390100_0400
rows.name: Well, I...

rows.label: bf08390100_0410
rows.name:
It's different for you, right?
You've been alive for a few centuries...

rows.label: bf08390100_0420
rows.name:
Did I ask you?
Homura, what do you think about it, really?

rows.label: bf08390100_0430
rows.name: Hey...

rows.label: bf08390100_0440
rows.name:
Sometimes I wondered why I have to
keep on living forever...

rows.label: bf08390100_0450
rows.name: ...Just on and on. No end in sight.

rows.label: bf08390100_0460
rows.name: But...

rows.label: bf08390100_0470
rows.name: ...it's different now.

rows.label: bf08390100_0480
rows.name: I'm glad I've stayed alive all this time.

rows.label: bf08390100_0490
rows.name:
Parting is always sad, but it's just part of the deal of
being me.

rows.label: bf08390100_0500
rows.name: Though...maybe...

rows.label: bf08390100_0510
rows.name:
...Maybe one day I'd be happy to close my eyes
forever...with someone special there by my side.

rows.label: bf08390100_0520
rows.name: Homura...

rows.label: bf08390100_0530
rows.name: That's our Homura.

rows.label: bf08390100_0540
rows.name:
Thanks, guys.
Thanks for sharing with me.

rows.label: bf08390100_0550
rows.name: So...what made you ask?

rows.label: bf08390100_0560
rows.name: I'm a Man-Eater.

rows.label: bf08390100_0570
rows.name: So... I don't know how long I'll live for.

rows.label: bf08390100_0580
rows.name: I mean, for all I know, I might just snuff it tomorrow.

rows.label: bf08390100_0590
rows.name: My lady...

rows.label: bf08390100_0600
rows.name:
But I can say this much.
My life and death isn't tied to any human.

rows.label: bf08390100_0610
rows.name: And?

rows.label: bf08390100_0620
rows.name: It's Shin.

rows.label: bf08390100_0630
rows.name: I've been wondering.

rows.label: bf08390100_0640
rows.name: Shin was collecting Core Crystals.

rows.label: bf08390100_0650
rows.name:
But why didn't he use them?
Doesn't he hate humans?

rows.label: bf08390100_0660
rows.name:
He could use them to create Blades,
then turn them into Man-Eaters.

rows.label: bf08390100_0670
rows.name:
He could expand Iira with
no need for humans in the mix.

rows.label: bf08390100_0680
rows.name: They do lack numbers. Is that all of them?

rows.label: bf08390100_0690
rows.name: Yeah. It's just the five of 'em. That's it.

rows.label: bf08390100_0695
rows.name:
When Metsu suggested getting Kamui and
Yoshitsune to resonate, Shin was dead against it.

rows.label: bf08390100_0700
rows.name:
So I think maybe...
Maybe Shin feels the same way as us...

rows.label: bf08390100_0710
rows.name: The same way as us...?

rows.label: bf08390100_0720
rows.name:
I think maybe that's why he won't
resonate with anyone.
